# ESLint Fix After Chat Completion

**When**: After chat finished code changes.

**Action**: Run ESLint auto-fix on changed apps.

## Command

From `backend/` (monorepo root):

```bash
npm run lint:fix
```

Runs `lint --fix` on project only.

Then `npm run affected` — lint, build, tests on all apps. Check output clean; fix errors; repeat until `npm run affected` passes.
